whatâ and the âwhyâ behind consumer purchases, from purchase motivations to on-shelf availability. \n\nBy connecting the ''why'' behind consumer decisions with Appetise Insights and Stock Checker''s real-time inventory tool, sales & marketing teams can finally tackle NPD challenges and OOS issues. "}'::jsonb, 'MEDIUM', NULL, '2025-09-17T02:09:06.000Z', '2025-10-02T02:56:18.601Z'),
