dpoint Management, RMM, and Patch Management, in G2''s Fall 2025 Report, and launched major product releases such as NinjaOne AI for Patch Sentiment and Mobile Device Management (MDM)[1][4][5].\n\nLEADERSHIP CHANGES:\nNo recent activity identified."}'::jsonb, '{"content":"NinjaOne, the automated endpoint management platform, delivers visibility, security, and control over all endpoints for more than 30,000 customers in 130+ countries.â¯â¯ \n\nâ¯â¯ \n\nThe cloud-native NinjaOne platform simplifies endpoint management, patching, and visibility for environments at any scale. It is proven to increase productivity, reduce security risk, and lower costs.â¯â¯ \n\nâ¯â¯ \n\nNinjaOne is obsessed with customer success and provides free and unlimited onboarding, training, and support. \n\nâ¯ \n\nTry NinjaOne for free atâ¯https://utm.io/uh6wFâ¯ "}'::jsonb, 'VERY HIGH', NULL, '2025-09-17T02:09:06.000Z', '2025-10-02T02:56:18.601Z'),
