mpany headcount has remained stable with only modest growth globally, and there are no reported sales/GTM hiring spikes attributed to Australia or Sydney locations in recent market signals[2].\n\nRECENT FUNDING:\n[GLOBAL] Vimeo has not announced any new investment rounds, financial milestones, or major funding events in the last 12 months. The company has previously reached public company status, and recent financial news does not highlight Australia or regional funding initiatives.\n\nRECENT ACHIEVEMENTS:\n[LOCAL] No local Australian or Sydney-specific awards, product launches, or partnerships announced for Vimeo in the last year. [REGIONAL] No APAC/ANZ recognitions or major milestones attributable to Vimeo found in recent news. [GLOBAL] Vimeo continues to be recognized for its professional video hosting features and privacy controls in the global market; it is positioned as a specialized platform for business and creative professionals, with ongoing feature improvements focused on quality-for-business use[1]. This status does not reflect any new, region-specific achievements in Australia.\n\nLEADERSHIP CHANGES:\n[LOCAL] No publicly reported executive appointments, promotions, or departures relating to Vimeo Australia or Sydney office, including sales, revenue, or people leaders, have been identified in the last year. [GLOBAL] Vimeo’s global leadership team remains stable with no major recent changes focusing on APAC or ANZ markets.\n\n[INDUSTRY] \n- The Australian software development sector continues to see steady growth in 2024-2025, particularly in SaaS, cloud services, and enterprise video tools.\n- Local competition for video hosting and collaboration software remains active, but no major industry changes uniquely impact Vimeo''s position in Sydney or Australia.\n- Industry trends in AU indicate increased enterprise investment in secure, customizable video solutions, which aligns with Vimeo’s global offering but does not signal recent local acceleration.\n\n**Summary:**\nVimeo does not appear to have initiated noteworthy business events, hiring, funding, achievements, or leadership changes specific to Sydney (or Australia/APAC) in the past 6-12 months. Global company developments continue, but none are directly tied to local operations at this time[1][2]. When seeking Sydney- or Australia-specific intelligence, market activity is minimal, and broader industry growth is the main signal relevant to the location."}'::jsonb, '{"content":"&lt;strong&gt;Sr. Account Executive&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Tokyo, Japan&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a Sr. Account Executive within the JAPAC Sales team, you will be responsible for selling Vimeo’s Enterprise video platform into some of the largest organisations in the JAPAC region. In this direct sales quota-carrying role, you will drive opportunities through the entire sales cycle from pipeline generation to closure, employing a value-oriented sales methodology.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Vimeo Sr. Account Executive is accountable for exceeding monthly and quarterly quotas, proactive deal management and forecast accuracy. A successful Sr. Account Executive is eager to learn, determined to adapt quickly, and comfortable with some ambiguity.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you''ll do:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Exceed Annual Recurring Revenue (ARR) targets by selling Vimeo Enterprise offerings: https://vimeo.com/enterprise&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Identify new growth opportunities for Japan/Korea/Taiwan&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Convey Vimeo’s unique value proposition to prospects and handle objections&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Position solutions against contending offerings in the marketplace&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Craft and negotiate enterprise-level proposals and contracts&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Maintain CRM data and pipeline within Salesforce.com&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Actively handle leads, generate pipelines and run campaigns to meet goals and objectives&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Support the RFI/RFP process by responding to business requirements&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills and knowledge you possess:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;6+ years of experience selling enterprise SaaS solutions and innovative technologies to large organisations with a proven track record of consistently exceeding quotas&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Proven success in introducing new concepts and building excellent client relationships at C-level within large enterprise organisations. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Account planning and territory management experience&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Previous Sales Methodology training (e.g. MEDDIC, SPIN, Value Selling)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Proven success navigating organisations and ability to quickly identify the decision-makers and the decision-making process for SaaS investments&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ability to operate with a sense of urgency and value accountability&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Excellent time management, organisational as well as presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ability to multi-task across multiple projects and internal partners&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of online video technologies, live streaming, advertising, payment, analytics, and technology companies&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Highly motivated and driven by results&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Vimeo (NASDAQ: VMEO) is the world''s most innovative video experience platform. We enable anyone to create high-quality video experiences to better connect and bring ideas to life. We proudly serve our community of millions of users – from creative storytellers to globally distributed teams at the world''s largest companies – whose videos receive billions of views each month. Learn more at www.vimeo.com.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Vimeo is headquartered in New York City with offices around the world. At Vimeo, we believe our impact is greatest when our workforce of passionate, dedicated people, represents our diverse and global community. We’re proud to be an equal opportunity employer where diversity, equity, and inclusion is championed in how we build our products, develop our leaders, and strengthen our culture."}'::jsonb, 'MEDIUM', 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEWOm5_36pwug/company-logo_200_200/B4EZdBBfP6GcAM-/0/1749142599174/vimeo_logo?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=L9ZjU6vq4P5hg8a-xdmX_X2fLzEASDf85Vn8k7E_hpg', '2025-09-29T14:14:47.000Z', '2025-10-02T02:56:18.602Z'),
