    ('recwJ1dv5GbuR1JJg', 'IBM', 'http://www.ibm.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ibm', 'Armonk, New York, NY, US', 'Information Technology & Services', '10001 -', '92', 'IBM is a global leader in information technology and services with a major presence in Australia and Singapore, operating in core tech sectors like AI, cloud, and automation. The company is actively expanding its channel partner ecosystem and has recently launched new SaaS products and AI-driven solutions, indicating strong growth and innovation. There is a robust sales leadership structure across APAC, including multiple Sales Directors and Regional Managers, providing direct access to key decision makers. These factors signal an immediate and high-probability opportunity for external recruitment support in sales and revenue roles.', true, false, '{"content":"RECENT TRIGGER EVENTS:\nIBM maintained its financial forecast during Q1 2025 despite economic uncertainty, citing significant growth in its generative AI (GenAI) business, which has reached $6 billion in business inception to date. The company also emphasized expansion in transforming offerings like hybrid cloud, AI, and automation, though some client decision-making on discretionary projects has slowed due to macroeconomic conditions as of April 2025.\n\nGROWTH SIGNALS:\nIBM is focusing on expanding its channel partner ecosystem, increasing revenue through channels, and enhancing partner technical skills in 2025. The company is emphasizing the scaling of AI and hybrid cloud services, and leaders project material financial impact from AI investments within the next one to two years.\n\nRECENT FUNDING:\nNo recent activity identified.\n\nRECENT ACHIEVEMENTS:\nIBM announced the launch of IBM Db2 and Db2 Warehouse SaaS on Azure with general availability on June 17, 2025, and the introduction of a Bring Your Own Cloud offering for Netezza SaaS on AWS, available June 2025. The company has also released new advancements in Turbonomic and Db2 platforms, highlighting product innovation in AI-driven cloud and data management solutions as of May 2025.\n\nLEADERSHIP CHANGES:\nNo recent activity identified."}'::jsonb, '{"content":"At IBM, we do more than work. We create. We create as technologists, developers, and engineers. We create with our partners. We create with our competitors. If you''re searching for ways to make the world work better through technology and infrastructure, software and consulting, then we want to work with you.\n\nWe''re here to help every creator turn their \"what if\" into what is. Let''s create something that will change everything."}'::jsonb, 'VERY HIGH', NULL, '2025-09-17T02:09:06.000Z', '2025-10-02T02:56:18.602Z'),
