iarity with customer success metrics, and the ability to analyze and interpret data to drive action &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience with CRM and customer engagement software (e.g. HubSpot, Intercom) &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Previous experience working with timesheet, payroll, or accounting software a bonus &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and remotely, with a strong work ethic and time management skills &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with our industry is a plus&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;"}'::jsonb, 'HIGH', 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D560BAQFtR8RniNWL0A/company-logo_200_200/company-logo_200_200/0/1704256166411/transvirtualtms_logo?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=tiSvK-mhaxYKQ5_0J5MnTx52Y5zrKlClhY5TFscusWs', '2025-10-01T14:23:17.000Z', '2025-10-02T02:56:18.602Z'),
